metadata.name: The Baron
metadata.description:
An exploration of the concept and social construct behind the lie. Who do we believe and who do we not? Is subjective truth and objective truth ultimately an irrelevant distinction? And how does nostalgia influence our memory? 

Only in one thing I am sure ...

The Baron would never lie!
